'''St. Anthony of Padua Parish''' - designated for [[Polish American|Polish immigrants]] in [[Fairfield, Connecticut]], [[United States]].

: Founded in 1927. It is one of the [[Polish-American Roman Catholic parishes in New England]] in the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Bridgeport|Diocese of Bridgeport]]. The architect of the 1970 church was [[Anthony J. DePace]] of New Yrok.

